    CASCADE NATURAL GAS PUBLIC MEETING Cascade Natural Gas will begin Phase 2 of the Anacortes High Pressure Replacement Project, replacing natural gas service lines in specific areas. This is an ongoing program to ensure customers safe and efficient natural gas service. During the construction phase crews will install mains and services in your neighborhood.
